Sure, here are some examples:

1. *Prilike* su se promenile u poslednjih nekoliko meseci. (The circumstances have changed in the last few months.)
2. Želim da iskoristim ove *prilike* i napredujem u karijeri. (I want to take advantage of these opportunities and advance in my career.)
3. Mogućnosti za putovanje su se otvorile, ali nemam *priliku* da putujem trenutno. (Travel opportunities have arisen, but I don't have the chance to travel at the moment.)
4. Ona je iskoristila svaku *priliku* da pokaže svoje znanje. (She took every opportunity to demonstrate her knowledge.)
5. U ovoj *prilici* želim da se zahvalim svima na podršci. (On this occasion, I want to thank everyone for their support.)
6. Nema *prilike* da se odmoriš ako želiš da ispunjavaš rokove. (There's no chance to rest if you want to meet the deadlines.)
7. Treba da se prilagodimo novim *prilikama* na tržištu. (We need to adapt to the new market conditions.)
8. U ovim teškim *prilikama* moramo da ostanemo jaki. (In these difficult times, we need to stay strong.)

Note: I have marked the word "prilike" with an asterisk (*) in each sentence. The translations are in parentheses.